            </h4>
            <p>
                NIDM and United Nations (Coordinated by UNOCHA) has planned a series of four regional trainings under the Capacity Building Programme (CBP) to be held at Quetta, Lahore, Gilgit and Peshawar. Officers from various provincial ministries, District Disaster Management Authorities (DDMAs) and line departments will participate in the trainings. Current phase of CBP will be completed in December, 2014.
