            <h4 class="media-heading text-capitalize">NIDM – DIPECHO Partner 7th Action (CBDRM ToT): September 2014</h4>
            <p>NIDM in collaboration with DIPECHO Partner 7th Action facilitated a five days Training of Trainer (ToT) on Community Based Disaster Risk Management (CBDRM) for the government officers from the selected districts of Sindh and KP provinces. The training took place at Islamabad from 8 – 12 September, 2014. NIDM took lead in organizing and facilitating the activity. Representatives of the country teams of various DIPECHO partner organizations including Save the Children, Care International, Malteser Internationl joined the process.</p>

