            <p>NIDM and international Organization for Migration (IOM), in collaboration with Provincial Disaster Management Authority (PDMA) KP organized five trainings on Camp Coordination and Camp Management (CCCM) in 2014. Officers from the DDMAs of Peshawar, Bannu, Lakki Marwat, and Kohat were trained in CCCM. The series of trainings included one Training of Trainers (ToT) held at Peshawar training fourteen (14) master trainers of CCCM. The master trainers trained will further pursue the CCCM agenda in the province.</p>

